      "content": "thanks for that but it actually still failed. the grader is using massive primes like 10^15 or something and it's timing out before it can finish. basically it needs to be way faster for those huge numbers. can u make it more efficient? if i dont get this passing by tonight i'm gonna fail the lab.",
